//
// Exercises BOTH sides of the runtime-guarded peel in one Python script:
// the IRON test.py JITs two designs (normal and zero) and dispatches each,
// validating that the zero-trip path completes without deadlocking on the
// producer-side lock.
//
// REQUIRES: ryzen_ai_npu2, peano, xrt_python_bindings
//
// RUN: %run_on_npu2% %python %S/test.py
